com.misc.common.moplaf.time.discrete

Interface TimeLine

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TimeLineImpl

    public interface TimeLine
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Time Line'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Bucket Type
    • Description
    • Time Zone ID
    • Locale Language
    • Locale Country
    • Horizon Start
    • Horizon End
    • Bucket
    • First Bucket
    • Last Bucket
    See Also:
    DiscretePackage.getTimeLine()
